Proactive Monitoring & Alerting Template - DevOps

1. Objective
Ensure DevOps proactively detects, monitors, and resolves issues across all environments before they impact other teams or customers.
Focus areas include:
* Monitoring automation
* PagerDuty alerts
* Structured communication
* Actionable thresholds

